      • assignedToUser

        public static java.util.List<Alarm> assignedToUser(AlarmAttendant attendant)
        Retrieve all Alarms from the database that has been assigned to the provided AlarmAttendant object. This method does not filter on open alarms only, instead it returns every alarm ever assigned to a particular user.
        Parameters:
        attendant - The AlarmAttendant user object for which assigned Alarms are to be retrieved
        Returns:
        A list of alarms if any are found. An empty list is returned otherwise.

      • openAlarmsAssignedToMobileCareTaker

        public static java.util.List<Alarm> openAlarmsAssignedToMobileCareTaker(AlarmAttendant caretaker)
        Retrieve all Alarms from the database that has been assigned from an AlarmAttendant to a Mobile Care Taker, which is an AlarmAttendant with role == 3.
        Parameters:
        caretaker - The AlarmAttendant object to query
        Returns:
        A list of open alarms assigned to an AlarmAttendant, where the attendant has role == 3:
